        <div class="value-card reveal">
          <div class="value-num">01</div>
          <h3>Climate Responsibility</h3>
          <p>We hold ourselves to the same environmental standards we help our clients achieve. Climate action is not a
            service — it is our ethos.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card reveal">
          <div class="value-num">02</div>
          <h3>Scientific Rigor</h3>
          <p>Every recommendation is evidence-based, aligned with the latest environmental science, and benchmarked
            against international standards.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card reveal">
          <div class="value-num">03</div>
          <h3>Systems Thinking</h3>
          <p>We understand that sustainability challenges are interconnected. We design solutions that address root
            causes, not symptoms.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card reveal">
          <div class="value-num">04</div>
          <h3>Community Integration</h3>
          <p>Sustainable development must benefit the communities it operates within. We embed social equity into every
            environmental strategy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card reveal">
          <div class="value-num">05</div>
          <h3>Transparent Impact</h3>
          <p>We measure, report, and communicate environmental impact with full transparency — holding ourselves and our
