        </div>
        <div class="value-card reveal">
          <div class="value-num">06</div>
          <h3>Innovation First</h3>
          <p>We continuously explore new tools, models, and frameworks to deliver cutting-edge sustainability solutions
            for a rapidly evolving world.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

